----More----
PageOneX is a tool build in Prcessing to scrap front page images from newspapers form kiosko.net, download them and build a matrix in .svg to be able to measure the surface dedicated to a a special thread.

See examples: http://numeroteca.org/cat/frontpage-newspaper/

Analyzing newspapers’ front pages to interpret the Mainstream Media ecology. Researching the #15M, #Occupy movement and the Arab Spring. Interested in the relationship between Mainstream Media and social Media (twitter).
Post: http://civic.mit.edu/blog/pablo/analyzing-newspapers-front-pages